---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Executive Summary">
    <section class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <h1 class="font-heading text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold tracking-tight text-pistos-black mb-6 leading-tight">
            Pistos: <span class="text-pistos-red">Digital Proposal Summary</span>
        </h1>
        <div class="bg-pistos-surface border border-pistos-border p-8 rounded border-l-4 border-l-pistos-black shadow-sm space-y-6">
            <div>
                <h2 class="font-heading text-xl font-bold text-pistos-black mb-2">What This Proposal Covers</h2>
                <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed text-pistos-muted">
                    This document outlines a digital strategy for <strong>Pistos</strong> — a business setup services company operating in the UAE. The proposal covers market positioning, competitor analysis, visual identity, and a phased execution plan for building the company's digital infrastructure.
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="border-t border-pistos-border pt-6">
                <h2 class="font-heading text-xl font-bold text-pistos-black mb-2">Market Position</h2>
                <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed text-pistos-muted">
                    After analyzing over 200 business setup firms in the UAE, it is clear that the top-tier agencies have moved beyond static websites. They now offer interactive tools, client portals, and structured content libraries. Pistos is positioned to serve serious entrepreneurs looking for reliable, long-term operational infrastructure — not just a trade license.
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="border-t border-pistos-border pt-6">
                <h2 class="font-heading text-xl font-bold text-pistos-black mb-2">The Two-Layer System</h2>
                <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed text-pistos-muted mb-4">
                    Rather than building everything at once, the project is structured as two independent layers:
                </p>
                <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-4 font-mono text-sm text-pistos-black">
                    <div class="border border-pistos-border rounded p-4 flex flex-col items-start space-y-2 bg-pistos-bg hover:border-pistos-black transition-colors">
                        <i data-lucide="globe" class="w-5 h-5 text-pistos-red"></i>
                        <span class="font-bold">Layer 1 — Public Website</span>
                        <span class="text-xs text-pistos-muted">Astro-based. Fast, credible, SEO-optimized. Focused on business setup lead capture.</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="border border-pistos-border rounded p-4 flex flex-col items-start space-y-2 bg-pistos-bg hover:border-pistos-black transition-colors">
                        <i data-lucide="lock" class="w-5 h-5 text-pistos-red"></i>
                        <span class="font-bold">Layer 2 — Client Portal</span>
                        <span class="text-xs text-pistos-muted">Next.js-based. Interactive tools, dashboards, and ecosystem cross-sell after onboarding.</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="border-t border-pistos-border pt-6">
                <h2 class="font-heading text-xl font-bold text-pistos-black mb-2">Ecosystem Integration</h2>
                <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed text-pistos-muted mb-4">
                    Pistos is the entry point into a wider group of companies. A client who starts with business setup can be naturally introduced to:
                </p>
                <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-4 font-mono text-sm text-pistos-black">
                    <div class="border border-pistos-border rounded p-4 flex flex-col items-start space-y-2 bg-pistos-bg hover:border-pistos-black transition-colors">
                        <i data-lucide="calculator" class="w-5 h-5 text-pistos-red"></i>
                        <span class="font-bold">The One Accountant</span>
                        <span class="text-xs text-pistos-muted">Tax & Audit Services</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="border border-pistos-border rounded p-4 flex flex-col items-start space-y-2 bg-pistos-bg hover:border-pistos-black transition-colors">
                        <i data-lucide="building" class="w-5 h-5 text-pistos-red"></i>
                        <span class="font-bold">DuneSaura</span>
                        <span class="text-xs text-pistos-muted">Real Estate & Workspaces</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="border border-pistos-border rounded p-4 flex flex-col items-start space-y-2 bg-pistos-bg hover:border-pistos-black transition-colors">
                        <i data-lucide="monitor-stop" class="w-5 h-5 text-pistos-red"></i>
                        <span class="font-bold">Mindcom</span>
                        <span class="text-xs text-pistos-muted">IT & Microsoft Cloud Solutions</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <p class="text-2xl font-heading mt-16 mb-8 text-center text-pistos-black leading-relaxed italic border-t border-b border-pistos-border py-8">
            "A digital presence that reflects the seriousness<br>and operational depth of the business."
        </p>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-4 mt-12 mb-32" data-aos="fade-up">
            <a href="/strategy" class="group border border-pistos-border rounded p-4 hover:border-pistos-red transition-colors text-center">
                <span class="text-xs text-pistos-muted block mb-1">01</span>
                <span class="font-heading font-bold text-sm text-pistos-black group-hover:text-pistos-red transition-colors">Strategy</span>
            </a>
            <a href="/competitors" class="group border border-pistos-border rounded p-4 hover:border-pistos-red transition-colors text-center">
                <span class="text-xs text-pistos-muted block mb-1">02</span>
                <span class="font-heading font-bold text-sm text-pistos-black group-hover:text-pistos-red transition-colors">Market</span>
            </a>
            <a href="/visuals" class="group border border-pistos-border rounded p-4 hover:border-pistos-red transition-colors text-center">
                <span class="text-xs text-pistos-muted block mb-1">03</span>
                <span class="font-heading font-bold text-sm text-pistos-black group-hover:text-pistos-red transition-colors">Identity</span>
            </a>
            <a href="/plan" class="group border border-pistos-border rounded p-4 hover:border-pistos-red transition-colors text-center">
                <span class="text-xs text-pistos-muted block mb-1">04</span>
                <span class="font-heading font-bold text-sm text-pistos-black group-hover:text-pistos-red transition-colors">Roadmap</span>
            </a>
        </div>
    </section>
</Layout>
